Midwest Investment Management | 401(k) Asset Management | Financial Advisor | Cleveland, Ohio - Home



























































Your Financial Advisor...



Midwest Investment Management is an independent, registered investment advisory firm based in Cleveland Ohio, serving individuals, 
            company retirement plans and 401(k) plans.
We believe that your financial advisor should be objective and 
            unbiased. Since we are not affiliated with any bank, brokerage firm 
            or insurance company, our firm provides independent 
            investment management services meeting your financial goals. 

The Partners of Midwest Investment Management
Seated (L-R) Norman F. Klopp, CFA, Meg E. Halloran, Keith A. Vargo, CFA
Standing (L-R) Elmer L. (Al) Meszaros, CFA, Robert J. Yaroma
Because every client’s investment management and asset management 
            goals are unique, our financial advisors do not offer off the shelf 
            “solutions” for your personal portfolio, 401(k) plan, trust, estate or 
            charitable account; instead we will meet with you, your accountant 
            and/or attorney to develop and implement a portfolio management and 
            asset management strategy suited to your individual needs, goals and 
            tax structure.
We will develop a portfolio that may include equities, fixed 
            income investments, mutual funds or perhaps all of those 
            vehicles—all under the watchful guidance of our experienced 
            portfolio managers.
As a client of Midwest Investment Management, we will work with you to develop an investment plan tailored to your specific needs. Your 
            financial advisor will maintain ongoing direct contact with you and 
            work toward establishing a trusted and long lasting relationship 
            with you.
Our portfolio management professionals have over 150 combined years of experience working with individuals, 401(k) plans, trust, estate and charitable trusts, throughout various investment and economic cycles. They are experienced professionals.


We invite you to learn about all the advantages a professional investment manager offers, by reviewing the information and data presented in this site. Then if you feel we are right for you, respond to any of our partners via e-mail or telephone.
Thank you













Midwest Investment Management - Cleveland, Ohio - Portfolio Management and Investment Advice - Norm Klopp







































Meg Halloran
Norm Klopp
Al Meszaros
Keith Vargo
Bob Yaroma




























Company Partners



Norman F. Klopp, Jr. Managing Partner
Norman F. Klopp, Jr. has responsibility for establishing investment policy, stock selection, and client portfolio management.
During his 40-year career, Mr. Klopp has established himself as a widely respected investment analyst and portfolio manager.
Mr. Klopp has been a repeat panelist on Wall Street Week With Louis Rukeyser, and when the popular television program was broadcast live from Cleveland, he was the only analyst invited to appear. Mr. Klopp has also appeared on the CNBC cable news network.
Our value investment philosophy can help investors increase their capital when the markets are moving upward, while trying to reduce their downside exposure when the markets drop, Mr. Klopp states.
Mr. Klopp is a graduate of Yale University and holds the CFA Institute’s Chartered Financial Analyst® designation—the industry’s highest standard for investment knowledge and ethics.  He is a member of the Cleveland Society of Security Analysts, and has served as a director of several privately held companies.
Mr. Klopp has served as a member and president of the Brecksville-Broadview Heights Board of Education, as a trustee of the Brecksville Towne Centre, a trustee of the Yale Alumni Association of Greater Cleveland, and as a trustee and president of the Achievement Centers For Children.  He and his wife, Sandy, reside in Brecksville and have two adult sons.
Mr. Klopp can be reached at 
								

